\n1801:                            \"pick a smaller model here when you want \"\r\n1802:                            \"Slot 1 != Slot 2 routing for VRAM headroom. \"\r\n1803:                            \"To use a remote OpenRouter model, set \"\r\n1804:                            \"OPENROUTER_API_KEY and \"\r\n1805:                            \"pick OpenRouter A/B (see docs/openrouter-setup.md).\"\r\n1806:                        ),\r\n1807:                    },\r\n1808:                ),\r\n1809:                \"custom_premise\": (\"STRING\", {\r\n1810:                    \"multiline\": True,\r\n1811:                    \"default\": \"\",\r\n1812:                    \"placeholder\": (\r\n1813:                        \"(optional) type a custom story premise here ƒ?\" \"\r\n1814:                        \"overrides the RSS news fetch\"\r\n1815:                    ),\r\n1816:                    \"tooltip\": (\r\n1817:                        \"Empty (default) -> RSS fetcher pulls a fresh \"\r\n1818:                        \"real-world science headline as the episode \"\r\n1819:                        \"seed.\\n\\n\"\r\n1820:                        \"Non-empty -> uses your text verbatim as the \"\r\n1821:                        \"seed and skips RSS entirely.\\n\\n\"\r\n1822:                        \"Use cases for the override:\\n\"\r\n1823:                        \"  - test a specific story idea\\n\"\r\n1824:                        \"  - reproduce a previous run with controlled \"\r\n1825:                        \"inputs\\n\"\r\n1826:                        \"  - work offline / skip RSS when the network \"\r\n1827:                        \"is slow.\"\r\n1828:                    ),\r\n1829:                }),\r\n1830:                \"include_act_breaks\": (\"BOOLEAN\", {\r\n1831:                    \"default\": True,\r\n1832:                    \"tooltip\": (\r\n1833:                        \"When ON (default), the outline LLM is told to \"\r\n1834:                      